tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE telemedicine_data (
  patient_id INT,
  visit_date DATE,
  institution_id INT,
  diagnosis TEXT,
  treatment_plan TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE TelemedicineData (
    patient_id INT,
    medical_condition VARCHAR(255),
    consultation_date TIMESTAMP,
    institution_id INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (patient_id, consultation_date)
);

CREATE TABLE telemedicine_data (
    patient_id UUID,
    date DATE,
    diagnosis VARCHAR,
    treatment_plan TEXT,
    PRIMARY KEY (patient_id, date)
)

CREATE TABLE research_institutions (
    institution_id UUID,
    name VARCHAR,
    location VARCHAR,
    PRIMARY KEY (institution_id)
)

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    collaboration_id UUID,
    patient_id UUID,
    institution_id UUID,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    PRIMARY KEY (collaboration_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES telemedicine_data(patient_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (institution_id) REFERENCES research_institutions(institution_id)
)

CREATE TABLE treatment_history (
    patient_id UUID,
    date DATE,
    treatment_given TEXT,
    outcome VARCHAR,
    PRIMARY KEY (patient_id, date),
    FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES telemedicine_data(patient_id)
)

CREATE TABLE telemedicine_data (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	patient_id INT NOT NULL,
	timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
	symptoms TEXT,
	diagnosis TEXT
);
